من هذه المنظمات وهذا هو الهجوم بشدة. الجمعيات النسائية في جامعة كاليفورنيا في بيركلي جعلها هدفهم لإعطاء المرأة مكانا لتشعر بالراحة وكذلك أفضل للمجتمع. مقارنة منازل محددة لشخصيات من فيلم عن البلطجة هي سخيفة وخارجة عن غير دقيقة. جعل الادعاء بأن الزمر الجمعيات النسائية هي غير مهينة والأخوة والقيم التي تأسست أنها جرا. ومن الواضح أن هذا طعنة في المجتمع في الحرم الجامعي الذي لا يفعل شيئا ولكن دعم بقية الجسم الطلابي.

Ut sodalis Graecas institutiones horum pars civitatis offensa abhorret. Ut ad scopum Sororities at UC Berkeley elit ac mulierum ad commune bonum. Cum in domo propria characteres ad a movie circa IMPORTUNUS est et absurdum, ultra millia. De hoc quod est sororities factiones sunt, et bona sunt condita in sorores deprimendo. Evidens est, quod non nisi in campo preponens societatem suscipere reliquum corpus discipulo.

ग्रीक समुदाय के एक सदस्य हैं और इन संगठनों में से एक के एक भाग के रूप में इस अत्यधिक आक्रामक है। यूसी बर्कले में महिला संघ यह महिलाओं सहज महसूस करने के साथ-साथ बेहतर समुदाय के लिए एक जगह देने के लिए अपने लक्ष्य बनाते हैं। बदमाशी के बारे में एक फिल्म से अक्षर के लिए विशिष्ट घरों की तुलना बेतुका और गलत से परे है। दावे कर रही है कि महिला संघ क्लिक्स हैं महिला संघ और मूल्यों वे पर स्थापित कर रहे हैं नीचा दिखा रहा है। यह स्पष्ट रूप से परिसर में एक समुदाय है कि लेकिन छात्र शरीर के बाकी का समर्थन कुछ भी नहीं है पर एक वार है।

As a member of the Greek community and a part of one of these organizations this is highly offensive. Sororities at UC Berkeley make it their goal to give women a place to feel comfortable as well as better the community. Comparing specific houses to characters from a movie about bullying is absurd and beyond inaccurate. Making the claim that sororities are cliques is demeaning the sisterhood and values they are founded on. This clearly is a stab at a community on campus that does nothing but support the rest of the student body.

What the fuck did you just fucking say about me, you little memer? I’ll have you know I rushed top of my class in Kappa Epsilon Kappa, and I’ve been involved in numerous philanthropy events on campus, and I have over 300 confirmed bids. I am trained in adorable fundraisers and I’m the top big in the entire Berkeley chapter. You are nothing to me but just another independent. I will wipe you the fuck out with greek social supremacy the likes of which has never been seen before on this Earth, mark my fucking words. You think you can get away with saying that shit to me over the Internet? Think again, fucker. As we speak I am contacting my secret network of sisters across the USA and your IP is being traced right now so you better prepare for the storm, maggot. The storm that wipes out the pathetic little thing you call your digital life. You’re fucking dead, kid. I can be anywhere, anytime, and I can kill your feed in over seven hundred ways, and that’s just with my Instagram account. Not only am I extensively trained in social media annihilation, but I have access to the entire readership of Total Sorority Move and I will use it to its full extent to wipe your miserable ass off the face of the Internet, you little shit. If only you could have known what unholy retribution your little “clever” meme was about to bring down upon you, maybe you would have held your fucking tongue. But you couldn’t, you didn’t, and now you’re paying the price, you goddamn idiot. I will shit fury all over you and you will drown in it. You’re fucking dead, kiddo.
